WEBVTT

00:00:00.830 --> 00:00:03.624
In the summer of 2014,

00:00:03.624 --> 00:00:09.422
I was in Iraqi Kurdistan
with a small team of archaeologists,

00:00:09.422 --> 00:00:14.594
finishing a season of field excavations
near the border town of Halabja.

00:00:15.428 --> 00:00:21.225
Our project was looking into something
which has puzzled and intrigued me

00:00:21.225 --> 00:00:24.270
ever since I began studying archeology.

00:00:24.729 --> 00:00:27.899
We're taught to believe
that thousands of years ago,

00:00:27.940 --> 00:00:31.569
when our ancestors
first invented agriculture